il]], Kuala Lumpur\n |attendance= \n |referee= \n}} \n\n=== Round 6 ===\nAll competition matches suspended.\n{{rugbybox collapsible |class=collapsible expanded |note-width=0 |date-width=18% |stadium-width=22% \n |date={{show by date|2020|04|26|Fri,|}} 24 April\n |time= {{resize|90%|7.15 pm [[Australian Western Standard Time|AWST]] ([[UTC+08:00|UTC+8]])}} \n |home= [[Western Force]] \n |score= \u2013\n |away= [[Manuma Samoa]] \n |report= \n |try1= \n |con1= \n |pen1= \n |cards1= \n |try2= \n |con2= \n |pen2= \n |card2= \n |stadium= [[Perth Oval|HBF Park]], Perth\n |attendance= \n |referee= \n}} \n\n{{rugbybox collapsible |class=collapsible expanded |note-width=0 |date-width=18% |stadium-width=22% \n |date={{show by date|2020|04|26|Fri,|}} 24 April\n |time= {{resize|90%|7.15 pm [[Hong Kong Time|HKT]] ([[UTC+08:00|UTC+8]])}}\n |home= [[South China Tigers]]\n |score= \u2013\n |away= [[Fijian Latui]]\n |report= \n |try1= \n |con1= \n |pen1= \n |cards1= \n |try2= \n |con2= \n |pen2= \n |card2= \n |stadium= [[Hong Kong Stadium|National Stadium]], Hong Kong\n |attendance= \n |referee= \n}}\n\n{{rugbybox collapsible |class=collapsible expanded |note-width=0 |date-width=18% |stadium-width=22% \n |date={{show by date|2020|04|26|Sun,|}} 26 April\n |time= {{resize|90%|[[Australian Central Standard Time|ACST]] ([[UTC+9:30|UTC+9.5]])}}\n |home= [[China Lions]]\n |score= \u2013\n |away= [[Malaysia Valke]] \n |report= \n |try1= \n |con1= \n |pen1= \n |cards1= \n |try2= \n |con2= \n |pen2= \n |card2= \n |stadium= [[Hindmarsh Stadium|Coopers Stadium]], Adelaide\n |attendance= \n |referee= \n}} <!--\n\n{{rubye|[[Fijian Latui]], [[South China Tigers]]}} -->\n\n=== Round 7 ===\nAll competition matches suspended.\n{{rugbybox collapsible |class=collapsible expanded |note-width=0 |date-width=18% |stadium-width=22% \n |date={{show by date|2020|05|04|Fri,|}} 1 May\n |time= {{resize|90%|6.45 pm [[Hong Kong Time|HKT]] ([[UTC+08:00|UTC+8]])}}\n |home= [[South China Tigers]]\n |score= \u2013\n |a